				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: The new poll, rl cash for in game objects....<a name="44094"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 4 04 5:54 AM</span></td>
