				<td colspan="2"><span>Again, I think some people have it wrong here.
<br />

<br />
SoE is asking if there should be a way, through them, to do legitimate account/character transfers between 2 parties.  Something they frown upon right now; though they don't do anything about it anymore, as best I can tell.
<br />

<br />
As it stands, people who do buy accounts are open to abuse/fraud/hijacking.  If you don't have the CD Key, the old owner can, at any time, get the account back.  What SoE is asking is if you would want them to broker such account sales to prevent such actions from taking place.  Also covers sales of ingame items.  It doesn't happen often, but you know if you buy something online via Ebay or such you could get screwed over.
<br />

<br />
No, I don't have any intention of buying an account from anyone, but I think it would be better if they did act as middle man and gave the account a new key when it was transfered.</span></td>
